data.description: New construction grey brick exterior with a grand foyer with double door entry way. Upgrades on this house include: outdoor kitchen and extended driveway. Family room features boxed ceilings with crown moulding. Kitchen offers an extended island and an upgraded appliance package. Master bathroom features dual vanities, 6'x4' extended shower with frameless glass. Single floor plan design with his and hers walk-in closets. Move in ready this August/September.
